      <div class="surface p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-dtc-primary">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Real-time manufacturing machine and system performance monitoring using Internet of Things</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2 italic">
          Miguel Saez, Francisco Maturana, Kira Barton, and Dawn Tilbury
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">
          Real-time performance monitoring system for manufacturing machines and systems using Internet of Things technologies and digital twin principles.
